data.description: Check out this beautifully forested neighborhood in Arlington that is right along the South Stillaguamish River! This rambler features vaulted ceilings, a circular kitchen, 2020 roof, new front porch, brand new interior paint, new light fixtures in both bathrooms, skylights and TONS of natural light. The yard is just shy of a 1/4 acre and has an adorable treehouse plus tons of trees including a fruiting peach tree! Hang out by the firepit or on oversized back deck, perfect for relaxing under the shady maple tree OR on the patio. Your choice! Frank Mason park is just down the road and affords you endless outdoor adventures, hiking, fishing & off-pavement expeditions. This property is move in ready and is just waiting for its new owners.
